instructions: Sign into your Fiber account with your Google Fiber Account credentials; then follow the prompts to schedule your installation appointment. You ll be directed to an online scheduler to select your appointment. If you're awaiting a transfer, the calendar displays two appointment types: Appointments marked in blue represent days we can transfer your phone number. Appointments marked in red represent days that we cannot transfer your phone number. If possible, choose an appointment on a day marked with blue. If you re unable to find an appointment that fits your schedule, click Notify me of new appointments . You ll receive updates about available appointments in the future.
